                <h1>Do Warrants Appear on Background Checks?</h1>
                <p>Warrants typically do show up on background checks, especially if the check is thorough. Criminal background checks can reveal active warrants, which may impact employment opportunities or other aspects of life. It is wise to be aware of any existing warrants and to seek legal advice if needed to address potential issues.</p>
